H0.text: The architectural term architrave refers to a. Molding

H1.text: The architectural term architrave refers to a. Pediment

H2.text: The architectural term architrave refers to a. Column

H3.text: The architectural term architrave refers to a. Lintel/beam

A4.text: The architrave is a style of mouldings framing a door, window or other rectangular opening

A5.text: The architrave is the lintel or beam that rests on the capitals of columns
